Mike Cooper and Peter Bengtsson nerding up an app at the
**Firefox OS App Days**.


This apps makes it possible for you to easily who owes who what for
group lunches. Sort of.


Running the server
------------------

Simple, just run it like this:

    $ cd server
    $ # create your virtualenv if you haven't done so
    $ pip install -r requirements.txt
    $ ./run.py

To run the server tests:

    $ cd server
    $ nosetests netsplit
